---
title: Tandoori Beef Tacos with Garlic & Mint Yoghurt
description: Take your favourite part of Indian flavours (tandoori) and the best handheld dinner around (tacos, of course) and you have the recipe for the next big thing in fusion food. With one bite of this crunchy salad, saucy beef, aromatic yoghurt and warm tortilla wraps, you'll get what we're taco-ing about!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-tandoori-tacos-cf3e5d75.jpg
